name: Jennifer Roberts
text: Have you ever wanted to get a pizza the way you want it?  Well go to Papa Murphy's Pizza!  You get to watch them make the specific pizza that you ordered, add or take off ingredients, and then you take it home and bake it so you know it's …More

name: Trent Somers
text: Its take and bake which is fun. The usually young girls that work the register and make the pizza are very friendly and accommodating. I have never had a bad experience here and have been here many times since they opened. Its creative pizzas for a good price made with fresh ingredients and a happy staff. Love papa murphies!

name: Shane Thee
text: I love Papa Murphy's and wish there was one closer to me. They are always clean and the staff are always friendly. Love their thin crusts and Chicago style pizzas.

name: Kitra Weaver
text: I love this place!  They have low calorie options & the pizza is wonderful!

name: Jay Cole
text: Best pizza around! Love the garlic sauce, quick and easy pick-up. Won't get pizza from anywhere else.

name: Bill jme
text: Sign up for the text message club to get good discounts... Fresh flavors, easy meal the whole family loves! Family sized stuff chicken bacon garlic is the best!

name: Mike Sierra Bravo
text: Good pizza ready to bake, lots of options, and always a great value. Do the survey while you wait for your pizza and have cookie dough for free!

name: Iris Cintron
text: I guess i didnt understand the term "take n bake" when i got there i was a bit surprised. When i got it home and it was cooked i can see why the pizza is expensive. Very delicious. However the customer service could be a lot better …More

name: Tim Lovitt
text: Great take home & bake pizza. Better then store bought & freshly made to your order..

name: Angela Ryals
text: We love stopping here on our way home!  Chicken garlic is the best!

name: H PO
text: My favorite take out pizza! Too bad i leave far away from the few stores they have in Central Florida!

name: Max B
text: The pizza was great, the experience was phenomenal, and it made my group pizza night. I'm used to okay pizza with pretty bad service, but my pep was delish and the girl at front, Ellie, was very kind to all of us.

name: Megan Stewart
text: Their food is delicious and if you sign up for  text messages you receive notifications on daily deals

text: Great pizza (try the double decker) and great staff service every time I've been there everybody that I've shown this place to goes back
